    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/21"
                            >Berengarius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >rex</rs>. Si at vota et legitimam nostrorum fidelium postulationem
                        aures clementie satagimus inclinare, devotiores eos ad nostram fidelitatem
                        efficimus, insuper ab eterno remuneratore premia sine fine mansura percipere
                        non ambigimus. Quapropter noverit universorum sancte Dei Ecclesie fidelium
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet et futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Archbishops" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/134"
                            >Landulfus</persName> venerabilem <rs key="#Archbishops"
                            >archiepiscopus</rs> sancte <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/147">Mediolanensis
                            ecclesie</placeName> suplicasset nostram clementiam, quatenus <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/133"
                            >Ermenulfi</persName> dilecto fideli nostro concederemus aliquantos <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave"
                            >servos</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_aldius"
                            >aldiones</rs> in <rs key="#Vici">vico</rs> et <rs key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/153">Luano</placeName>
                        pertinentibus de iure regni nostri, idest nomina eorum: <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Other_clerics"
                            >Deusdedi</persName>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Other_clerics"
                            >clerico</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Brother_of"
                            >germanis suis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Legally_recognised_union_with"
                            >uxores illorum</rs> cum agnitione illorum et <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >Ursone</persName> cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Legally_recognised_union_with"
                            >uxore sua</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Son_of #Daughter_of"
                            >filiis et filias</rs> nec non et <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >Lupone</persName> cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Legally_recognised_union_with"
                            >uxore</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Son_of #Daughter_of"
                            >filiis et filias</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Nephew_of #Niece_of"
                            >nepotis</rs>. Cuius precibus assensu prebentes, ea videlicet que iuste
                        et legaliter nos est deprecatus, inde hoc strenuitatis nostre preceptum
                        fieri decrevimus, per quod predictus fidelis noster Ermenulfus eosdem servis
                        et ancillis, aldiones vel aldianas superius nominatis cum omni iure
                        adiacentiis et pertinentiis earum, que sunt <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >casis</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >universis territoriis mobilibus et inmobilibus</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >Florane</persName> cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius #Daughter_of"
                            >filias suas</rs> et possessiones illarum, omnia et ex omnibus seu per
                        aliis singulis locis de ipsis aut eorum iure pertinentes inventum fuerit
                        iuste et legaliter ad ipsis servis et aldionibus superius nominatis futuris
                        temporibus absque ullius contradictione perpetualiter tam ipse predictus
                        fidelis noster Ermenulfus quam sui heredes possideant, liberam quoque et
                        firmissimam in omnibus habeant <rs
                            key="#Houses #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Royal_slave #Royal_aldius"
                            >potestatem donandi, ordinandi, comutandi, vendendi</rs>, seu quovis
                        titulo inscripcionis alienandi, remota tocius publice potestatis
                        inquietudine. Si quis vero, quod minime credimus, quicumque temerarius
                        contra hoc nostrum regali preceptum quandoque tempore insurgere aut
                        inrumpere temptaverit, sciat se compositutum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras XX</rs>, meditatem palatio nostro et reliquam medietatem sepe
                        fato Ermenulfo suisque heredibus ac proheredibus. Ut autem ab omnibus verius
                        credatur et diligentius observetur, manu propria supter firmavimus et anulo
                        nostro inpressione insigniri iussimus. Signum domni Berengarii gloriosissimi
                        regis. <persName key="#Notary">Restaldus</persName> notarius iussione regia
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/58">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data XV kal. Mar., anno
                        incarnationis Domini DCCCXCVIII, anno vero regni domni Berengarii
                        gloriosissimi regis X, indictione prima. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/147">Mediolano</placeName> in
                            <orgName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/95">monasterio
                            Sancti Ambrosii</orgName>. In Dei nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
